                </li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai-positron-code-development.dita" xtrc="li:6;176:21">
                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai-positron-code-development.dita" xtrc="p:14;177:24"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai-positron-code-development.dita" xtrc="b:18;177:27">Refactor Complex Code with <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai-positron-code-development.dita" xtrc="i:6;177:57">Suggest Refactoring</i></b> - If you have a
                        monolithic template such as: </p>
                    <codeblock id="codeblock_zzt_hhf_bgc" xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai-positron-code-development.dita" xtrc="codeblock:9;179:59">&lt;xsl:template match="book"&gt;
