                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai-positron-code-development.dita" xtrc="p:17;220:24">By breaking the logic into separate templates for &lt;book&gt;, &lt;chapter&gt;,
                        and &lt;section&gt;, each template is focused on a single responsibility. This
                        modular approach makes it easier to understand what each part of the code is
                        doing, and to locate or update specific logic. </p>
